on is summarized. The emphasis is placed primarily on the experimental\nwork and interpretation of the reaction data, but discussions of the theory and\nastrophysics are also pursued. The main goal is to summarize and clarify the\ncurrent understanding of the reaction and then point the way forward to an\nimproved determination of the reaction rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Sep 2017 17:25:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-12"}
