 spherical anisotropy parameter $\\beta$,\ndark matter fraction, as well as inner density slopes for the stellar, dark\nmatter and total mass distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Sep 2017 11:57:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
